WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:09.150
Hey, good morning family, or afternoon, or evening, or good night, or wherever you are in the world. I have some things I want to talk to you all about.

00:00:09.151 --> 00:00:21.508
If you go back to the word I gave ten months ago or more—it’s probably about a year or so ago now—whenever the Lord showed me the dollar crashing.

00:00:21.509 --> 00:00:36.959
I’m going to go over that again. He warned me that there’s going to be a major global shaking of finances, bringing forth digital platforms.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:54.768
This is what he told me about a year ago. I was praying and I saw a flagpole with a $100 bill on it. It was moving back and forth, and I saw digital writing.

00:00:54.769 --> 00:01:04.043
It looked like digital code in this $100 bill, and it was alive and moving, kind of like stocks, but it was digital.

00:01:04.044 --> 00:01:11.563
It was like crypto writing. Do you know what I’m talking about, son? Okay, so it was moving like that.

00:01:11.564 --> 00:01:49.438
Then I said, "Lord, what are you showing me?"And he said, "The dollar is about to turn into a digital dollar, and it will be worth half of the purchasing power of what it used to be."I saw it was at 50 cents—purchasing power of 50 cents to a dollar—because of inflation and the things happening with America and the economy.

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:53.780
Then he showed me what was going to happen: the banking sector.

00:01:53.781 --> 00:02:06.502
All the major banks—Chase Bank, Wells Fargo, you name it, the huge world banks—all seized the money inside of the banks.

00:02:06.503 --> 00:02:17.028
It was like it went into a bail-in. I don't know what you would call that. Like I said, I'm not real educated on stuff like this.

00:02:17.029 --> 00:02:24.535
I saw all the money being seized inside of the banks, and you weren't allowed to withdraw any of it.

00:02:24.536 --> 00:02:36.716
People were furious because they couldn't get their money out; the banks kept it. When this happened, the dollar crashed.

00:02:36.718 --> 00:02:52.893
Then they took all the notes on the homes and the car loans, everything, because people couldn't make their payments anymore since the dollar had collapsed.

00:02:52.894 --> 00:03:08.980
I saw people's car notes and car loans wiped out, kind of like it was with student loans back whenever the big COVID happened.

00:03:08.981 --> 00:03:24.639
They weren't allowed to collect those student loans; they froze all that for several years, and people weren't made to pay those payments anymore.

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:32.238
That's what it was like with the housing market or the car loans. They didn't come and foreclose on everybody.

00:03:32.239 --> 00:03:42.655
They didn't say, "Hey, you're out."They just froze it across the board because they didn't make everybody make their payments, just like it was with student loans.

00:03:42.656 --> 00:03:47.569
That's what I saw; I did not see any more of what happened afterward.

00:03:47.570 --> 00:03:52.589
People say, "Well, this is a debt jubilee."I didn't see it like that. That's what I'm trying to say.

00:03:52.590 --> 00:03:58.273
I don't want to add anything to or take anything away from this prophetic word.

00:03:58.274 --> 00:04:04.318
I just want to tell you what the Lord showed me. Then the Lord showed me people who were dressed up.

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:24.564
Because it happened so quickly—kind of like I told you all about the four oak trees—if you go back to the prophetic word that I gave, the dream I had about the four oak trees, four years or four months or four whatever it was, each oak tree represented, I believe, a year.

00:04:24.565 --> 00:04:30.900
Now, some people say it's a season because of what I saw, and some people say it is whatever. It's your interpretation.

00:04:30.901 --> 00:04:46.239
I just told you all to pray about it and see what the Holy Spirit tells you concerning these things that the Lord shows me, because I see in part and hear in part, and I'm a work in progress just like everybody else.

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:52.156
But if the Lord's telling me to tell you something, I want you to pray about it and see what he's telling you.

00:04:52.157 --> 00:05:02.376
I saw people in nice clothes because it happened just like I told you; it happened like winter came onto the trees, they lost all their leaves, and everything happened suddenly.

00:05:02.377 --> 00:05:19.068
People were standing in line trying to find groceries. They were trying to get groceries at the store, but there was no food. Remember I told you there were cobwebs on the shelves?

00:05:19.069 --> 00:05:35.982
I could see cobwebs in the corners of these shelves in the grocery stores, which I believe represented quite some time passing, because cobwebs don't happen in the corners of a grocery store shelf unless it's over time.

00:05:35.983 --> 00:05:43.537
It doesn't happen overnight. There were shelves that were completely bare in these grocery stores.

00:05:43.538 --> 00:05:52.956
People were lined up trying to get whatever they could in paper sacks or whatever they had, but like I said, they had nice clothes on.

00:05:52.957 --> 00:05:57.196
They weren't dressed dirty, but they were all lined up for a mile long.

00:05:57.197 --> 00:06:05.340
They wrapped around the buildings and down the street, waiting just to get into that store.

00:06:05.341 --> 00:06:10.922
He told me the Euro would be in trouble because of what was going on with Europe and this war.

00:06:10.923 --> 00:06:17.994
That was one of the first signs that this was all going to happen like dominoes.

00:06:17.995 --> 00:06:25.934
It's interesting because as I go along with my giftings and what the Lord has shown me, he gives me more and more each time.

00:06:25.935 --> 00:06:52.563
Even in what I told you last time about how China made a trade war with America, and all the supplies from China were not coming over in the big ships anymore because of the war escalating—I believe it has to do with Taiwan and what's coming in the future—he shows me a little bit more.

00:06:52.564 --> 00:07:05.720
If you go back and watch those other prophetic words, it's like putting a puzzle together one piece at a time.

00:07:05.721 --> 00:07:11.885
So, I saw the digital dollar, the crashing of the economy, and the oak trees.

00:07:11.886 --> 00:07:18.665
Remember, I also told you about all the people rioting after the dollar crashes?

00:07:18.666 --> 00:07:34.205
The government was not able to give them their Social Security checks, welfare, food stamps, or entitlements.

00:07:34.206 --> 00:07:42.241
They were all upset. They had their signs and were going through like a Million Man March. There were tons of them.

00:07:42.242 --> 00:08:01.394
Literally hundreds of thousands of people were taking to the streets, rioting and pillaging, stealing from stores, carrying their signs and going down the streets demanding what they felt they were rightfully owed.

00:08:01.394 --> 00:08:15.359
Then they brought in the National Guard. The Lord showed me all this in a vision: Hummers and chain-link barbed wire fences through major cities with checkpoints.

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:25.519
They put in martial law because of the people rioting in New York, Chicago, and all up north—and basically everywhere.

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:31.326
I’m not going to say it was just the Northeast; it was everywhere in America.

00:08:31.327 --> 00:08:43.168
People were acting a fool because they couldn't get their free handouts for food and whatever. That was part of what happens when the dollar crashes.

00:08:43.169 --> 00:08:54.034
Like I said, I'm adding each piece of the puzzle of what the Holy Spirit has warned me, and I keep getting more.

00:08:54.034 --> 00:09:03.214
Even again tonight, the Lord talked about the great Ichabod and said there's a great Ichabod fixing to take place.

00:09:03.215 --> 00:09:09.520
He said people call Him, "Lord, Lord,"but their hearts are far from Him.

00:09:09.521 --> 00:09:29.695
He said, "You will see a separation between the tares and the wheat; you're going to see this."And the ones that are true believers right now, who are truly on fire for me and have a relationship with me and that truly are—I have been their Lord.

00:09:29.696 --> 00:09:39.590
He said, "You will see this, and there is going to be a great apostasy even greater than what we've seen right now.

00:09:39.591 --> 00:09:46.498
We're about to see a greater separation between the tares and the wheat.

00:09:46.499 --> 00:09:52.464
You're going to see this in the days ahead because people are going to really know.

00:09:52.465 --> 00:10:00.022
You're going to know the real Christians from the people who are just lip service from the real true hearts.

00:10:00.023 --> 00:10:12.469
There is a purification coming. There is a refiner's fire coming to the body of Christ, and there will be a shaking coming.

00:10:12.470 --> 00:10:18.914
I got corrected on my grammar; there is no such thing as a 'shakening.'You know what?

00:10:18.915 --> 00:10:28.836
I'm going to say shaking. Sorry, Mr. Grammar Police. There's a great shaking.

00:10:28.837 --> 00:10:38.804
Don't watch my video, go away then. Bye-bye. But there's going to be this stuff take place, and I hope you're part of it.

00:10:38.805 --> 00:10:47.748
You're probably going to be the grammar police; you're probably the one that's getting shaken because these people don't know Jesus.

00:10:47.749 --> 00:10:56.919
A lot of them don't, but they think they do. But we're going to see the separation between the goats and the sheep. Watch.

00:10:56.920 --> 00:11:11.113
You're going to see all this: the people who are on fire and the people who are lukewarm, because a lot of you think that you're on fire and you're as cold as a cold stove, and you don't have any part of the Holy Ghost inside of you.

00:11:11.114 --> 00:11:17.561
You're so far away from it. I'm telling you, it's coming. You're going to see this in the days ahead.

00:11:17.562 --> 00:11:24.723
It is going to be a lot of people; they have their nose turned up toward God, and there is going to be a great humbling coming.

00:11:24.724 --> 00:11:42.276
This was something that was alarming to me because tonight in prayer, he showed me again about the dollar crash—another thing warning me about a major shaking that's about to take place soon.

00:11:42.277 --> 00:11:46.976
People say, 'When is this going to happen?'You're going to have to ask the Lord about that yourself.

00:11:46.977 --> 00:12:12.439
I have my thoughts, and I believe 2025 is going to be a dark year because of the dam that I saw with Joe Biden and all the things they were trying to hold back from being released after the elections.

00:12:12.440 --> 00:12:32.637
