00:13:03.976 --> 00:13:10.956
We're going to see a digital currency; it'll be like crypto, and we're going to see this happen very soon.

00:13:10.957 --> 00:13:16.154
I really believe that we're seeing the beast system being set up right before our eyes.

00:13:16.155 --> 00:13:23.939
And if you're not watching and your head is in the sand, God help you because we're there, folks.

00:13:23.940 --> 00:13:31.503
Jesus is getting ready to come back, and he's coming back very soon.

00:13:31.504 --> 00:13:51.199
I'm putting all these things together: the major earthquake, the tumbleweeds coming down the New York Stock Exchange.

00:13:51.200 --> 00:14:01.295
I've seen so many different things about the dollar. And like I said, not financial advice, but he showed me things happening with gold and silver.

00:14:01.296 --> 00:14:05.399
