00:15:21.406 --> 00:15:29.154
I said, 'Lord, where's the new word? What are you doing? Are you not going to give me a new word?'He said, 'Brandon, you don't need a new word right now.

00:15:29.155 --> 00:15:40.105
Focus on what I've told you. Pray about what I've already said to you and take it seriously, for the hour is short.

00:15:40.106 --> 00:15:52.826
You don't need a new word of the day; seek me for what I've already told you.'He said, 'Brandon, they're getting something new all the time on these other channels that are false prophetic words.

00:15:52.827 --> 00:15:58.719
