00:16:46.647 --> 00:16:57.371
I'm excited about the revival, but I know there's a great shaking coming, and it's going to shake America for the upcoming revival.

00:16:57.372 --> 00:17:06.067
God bless you all. Let me pray for you. Father, I just thank you for every single person who is watching this channel right now.

00:17:06.068 --> 00:17:18.037
I pray peace over them, that they're not tormented by fear. But we are watchmen; we are listening, waiting, hearing your voice.

00:17:18.038 --> 00:17:30.208
And I thank you, Lord, just like you told Joseph there would be seven years of plenty and seven years of famine. Father, I thank you that you speak to people still today.

